            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1327378227,
            "creation_date": 1327378227,
            "body": "<p>What the code is trying to do is format the spaces<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>%-5s\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>will add extra spaces <strong>at the end<\/strong> of the word to complete 5 character. For example if you have:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.format(\".%-5s.\",\"cat\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>the output will be<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>.cat  .\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Now, if you have <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>%5s\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>it will add spaces <strong>before<\/strong> the word to complete 5 characters. So with a similar example:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.format(\".%5s.\",\"cat\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>the output will be<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>.  cat.\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
